STATE
v.
Nijel Ramsey LEE. No. 416P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Jan. 28, 2016. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Nijel Ramsey Lee, Brunswick, for Lee, Nijel Ramsey. R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of December 2015 by Defendant for Notice of Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 28th of January 2016."
